    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "Reference is made to Bureau letter dated July 21, 1947, addressed",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "to Mrs. [REDACTED] Hicksville, Long Island, New",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "York, a copy of which was sent to the New York Office.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "Mrs. [REDACTED] was interviewed by Special Agent [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "on August 12, 1947, at which time she advised that this coded message had",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "appeared in \"Newsday,\" the local newspaper of Nassau and Suffolk County,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "Long Island, New York. She stated that the message had appeared in the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "\"County Irritant,\" a feature of this paper, and had been signed \"Radio Ham.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "Mr. [REDACTED] of \"Newsday,\" Hempstead, New York,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "was interviewed and advised that this article had been sent to the newspaper",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "by letter which was signed \"Radio Ham,\" and explained that he had no way of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "determining the identity of the writer. Mr. [REDACTED] stated that it was his",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "opinion that the code had been made up by some local \"screwball\" who had",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "been affected by all of the newspaper publicity that had been given at that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "time to the story about flying discs.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "There is enclosed an article appearing in the July 12th issue of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "\"Newsday\" concerning this coded message, which might be of interest in this",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "matter.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "Unless advised to the contrary, no further effort is being made",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
